IN the INTEREST OF L.C., A Juvenile. (L.C.-Petitioner) C-361 September Term 2017
079968 Supreme Court of New Jersey. December 1, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000537-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
